<h3><p style="text-align: center">PREFACE</h3>

<div style="position: absolute; left: 0; right:0; margin:auto;">
\image image2
</div>
<div style="position:relative;">

<p>The climate of today's world is quite unfavorable. Man is using the natural resources very destructively. He is not thinking about the environment and others. Even, he is destructing himself because of his personal greed. 
<p>Temperature is rising with a high rate. Environment is being polluted. It is being degraded without any bounds. Global Warming is increasing day-by-day. Various people, organizations, etc are overusing / misusing the natural resources without thinking for the future state of environment and needs of future generation.
<p>As we look into the environment and climate of today's world, we will come to know that our earth is in a great danger. There is a high danger on each and every creature of this planet if the present destructive deeds of man are not stopped.
<p>So, I find a way to help my environment and my fellow creatures through this presentation. I hope this will affect and make the common mass, especially of Aonla region, aware of their surroundings and they will help their own mother earth to get rid of the curse of pollution.
<p>
<p>Actually this was made by me when I was not given EVS. I was inspired by my grandfather, Prof. Giriraj Nandan, who is a great historian of Aonla. He has written numerous books on the history of Ruhelkhand and its constituent cities including Aonla. He has written history on other places too.
<p>But our area of interest is different. He loves history while I love Environment. So I made it. And I found its features similar to those given in Unit 6, Ch. 2 ('s syllabus). So I include this in this book.
<p>This presentation / case study was completed by June 2011.

<p style="text-align: right"><i><b>Arya Tanmay Gupta</b></i>
</div>

